Id-1: Login with valid email and pass

Steps:
1. Open http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Find "Email" field
3. Input "Student" into "Email" field
4. Find "Password" field
5. Input "909090" into "Password" field
6. Find "Вход" button
7. Click on "Вход" button

Expected result: Main page is displayed. Valid avatar is displayed in the top left corner of the page


Id-2: Logout from account

Precondition: User must be logged in (use Id-1 test case)

Steps:
1. Find dropdown user menu at the top right corner of the page
2. Click on dropdown user menu
3. Find "Выход" button
4. Click on "Выход" button

Expected result: Login page is displayed


Id-3: Create new item in "Аппарат"

Precondition: User must be logged in (use Id-1 test case)

Steps:
1. Find "Словари" item at the sidebar menu
2. Click on "Словари" item
3. Find "Аппарат" item at the treeview menu
4. Click on "Аппарат" item
5. Find "Add" button
6. Click on "Add" button
7. Find "Apparat number" field
8. Input in "Apparat number" field "test" value
9. Find "Apparat comment" field
10. Input in "Apparat comment" field "comment" value
11. Find "Создать" button
12. Click on "Создать" button

Expected result: New apparat "test" with comment "comment" is created


Id-4: Delete item from "Тип запчастей"

Precondition: User must be logged in (use Id-1 test case)

Steps:
1. Find "Словари" item at the sidebar menu
2. Click on "Словари" item
3. Find "Тип запчастей" item at the treeview menu
4. Click on "Тип запчастей" item
5. Find "Add" button
6. Click on "Add" button
7. Find "Spare type name" field
8. Input in "Spare type name" field "test" value
9. Find "Создать" button
10. Click on "Создать" button
11. Find "test" item in the table "Device list"
12. Click on "test" item in the table "Device list"
13. Find "Удалить" button
14. Click on "Удалить" button

Expected result: "test" item was deleted from table "Device list"


Id-5: Delete item from "Тип запчастей"

Precondition: User must be logged in (use Id-1 test case)

Steps:
1. Find "Словари" item at the sidebar menu
2. Click on "Словари" item
3. Find "Сотрудники" item at the treeview menu
4. Click on "Сотрудники" item
5. Find "Add" button
6. Click on "Add" button
7. Find "Worker surname" field
8. Input in "Worker surname" field "Surname" value
9. Find "Worker name" field
10. Input in "Worker name" field "Name" value
11. Find "Worker middle name" field
12. Input in "Worker middle name" field "Middle-name" value
13. Find "Worker phone" field
14. Input in "Worker phone" field "111111111" value
15. Find "Создать" button
16. Click on "Создать" button
17. Find "Surname Name Middle-name" item with phone "111111111" from "Сотрудники" list
18. Click "Surname Name Middle-name" item with phone "111111111" from "Сотрудники" list
19. Find "Worker phone" field
20. Input in "Worker phone" field "000000000" value
21. Find "Сохранить" button
22. Click on "Сохранить" button

Expected result: "Surname Name Middle-name" item now is with phone "000000000"